title: Grateful Dead Live at Wallace Wade Stadium, Duke University on 1971-04-24
lineage: 2nd (possibly 3rd) Generation Reels (Technics RS-1506) > Apogee Mini Me (24-bit/96k) > Adobe Audition 3.01 (24-bit/96k)> TLH flac2496
description:
Set I
Truckin', Deal, Hard To Handle, Me And Bobby McGee, Bertha, Playin' In The Band, Cumberland Blues, Next Time You See Me, Loser, Sugar Magnolia, Casey Jones
Set II
Good Lovin'-> Drums-> Good Lovin', Me & My Uncle, Sing Me Back Home, Greatest Story Ever Told-> Johnny B. Goode, Not Fade Away-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Not Fade Away, Uncle John's Band

Comment
"Joe College Weekend" - Other artist(s): Butlerfield Blues Band: NRPS; Beach Boys
